title: ELEGANT AN DMODERN BRICKELL FLATIRON!!
posting_body: ['Welcome home to your elegant and modern 1 bedroom with den.', 'Boasting 2 full baths and a balcony with unparalleled city views this barely lived in apartment is one to envy.', 'The best 1 bedroom line in the Brickell Flatiron offers ample closet space, state of the art appliances not limited to a washer dryer, dishwasher and more.', 'Central air throughout and privacy curtains deliver the ultimate in comfort and luxury.', 'The Brickell Flatiron is the newest premier high rise in Miami’s most desired neighborhood.', 'Enjoy swimming or relaxing on your roof top terrace, work out in the professional fitness center, or take a dip on the lower lap pool.', 'A full service staff welcome you and provide the utmost in security.', 'Pets are case by case.', 'Take advantage of 24/7 valet parking.', 'all units are one year lease min!', 'credit score close to 700 or higher required, proof of income 2,5 greater than rent price, first month + last month + security deposit to move in!', 'Dilya Taveras', 'Equity Realty', 'TEXT :', 'show contact info']
